column2: SELECT TOP #   e.SystemStudentID as StudentID,   e.GradeLevel as EnrollmentGrade,   e.SchoolYear4Digit as SchoolYear4Digit,   t.TestPeriod as Period,   t.TestSubjectGroup as AssessmentSubject,   e.SystemStudentID as MetricSource,   t.TestType as MetricName,   t.TestScore as Score,   t.TestDate as IsMostRecent FROM Enrollment as e INNER JOIN TestScores as t   ON e.SystemStudentID = t.SystemStudentID INNER JOIN ParentEngagement as p   ON e.SystemStudentID = p.StudentID INNER JOIN EmotionalScreener as s   ON e.SystemStudentID = s.StudentID
